Package: aurora
Type: Package
Title: Multimodal Data Integration for Weather, Economics, and GDELT
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zaed Khan
Maintainer: Zaed Khan <zaed@example.com>
Description: Tools to fetch, aggregate, and merge daily weather data from Open-Meteo, 
    economic indicators from FRED, and event data from GDELT into a unified 
    macroeconomic dataframe.
